profile:
Weekends and your leisure time were not made for cleaning, why not have us do all of your housework for you?  Housework is a big task, and with school, kids and work it can seem impossible.  We can offer to you the best in house cleaning and competitive rates!
 
  Top To Bottom Cleaning is a cleaning company that can offer you the best and most thorough clean in Peterborough and the Kawarthas.
 
 
We offer competitive rates for all types of cleaning, including:
 
Weekly- Bi-Weekly - Monthly etc
Special event preparation or clean-up
Spring cleaning
Move-out/move-in
One time cleanings
And more!
 
ALL products are supplied by us.  You worry about nothing!  Special request and green products can also be used.
 
To request an estimate contact us today! 

Bonded & Fully insured for your peace of mind

Gift certificates also available!

Call Jessica at 705-927-2969 or e-mail jessica@toptobottomcleaning.org
